metadata.description:
"Water Tiger" is number 1 of 60 NFTs
under Digital Zodiac. A
reinterpretation of the Chinese Zodiac by MAHH_ART

The "Water Tiger" is the first collection in Digital Zodiac. the Tiger itself Represent power, courage, confidence, leadership and strength. And the Water itself represent intelligence and wisdom, flexibility, and softness.
